-- Music Licensing Group, Mobile Carriers Close to Royalties Deal
-- B y   D o n   J e f f r e y
-- 2010-10-26T16:07:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-26/music-licensing-group-mobile-carriers-close-to-royalties-deal.html
Music-licensing organization ASCAP
is close to a settlement with two of the largest mobile phone
companies, Verizon Communications Inc. and Ericsson Inc., on
rates to be paid for providing music over wireless devices,
lawyers for both sides said today in court in New York.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Donald Jeffrey in New York at 
